<h1 class="header animated fadeIn"><a>Privacy Policy</a></h1>

<div class="container-flex legal-content">
  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Last Updated: February 2026
    </p>
    <p class="textiboi">
      This Privacy Policy describes how the Focus application ("the App")
      handles your information. LeonimusT is committed to protecting your
      privacy and ensuring transparency about our data practices.
    </p>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we handle
      your data when you use our App.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Data Storage - Local Only</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      The Focus app is designed with privacy and offline use as core
      principles. All user data (such as focus session settings and local
      timers) is stored <strong>locally on your device only</strong>. This
      means:
    </p>
    <ul class="textiboi">
      <li>Your focus session information never leaves your device</li>
      <li>We do not have access to your session data</li>
      <li>Your data is not uploaded to any servers or cloud services</li>
      <li>No user accounts are created or maintained</li>
      <li>We cannot see, access, or recover your data</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Your data remains entirely under your control on your personal device.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">External Network Requests</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      The Focus App is designed to work offline and does not make external
      network requests as part of its normal operation. No personal data or
      session information is transmitted over the network by the App.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">No Data Collection</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We want to be completely transparent: The Focus app does NOT collect,
      transmit, store, or process any of the following:
    </p>
    <ul class="textiboi">
      <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone number,
        etc.)</li>
      <li>Device identifiers or unique user IDs</li>
      <li>Usage analytics or behavior tracking data</li>
      <li>Location data</li>
      <li>Contact lists or address books</li>
      <li>Crash reports or diagnostic data (unless you explicitly opt-in and
        the App provides such an option)</li>
      <li>Any other personal or sensitive information</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Since we don't collect any data by default, we have nothing to share,
      sell, or use for marketing purposes.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">No Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      The App does not integrate with any third-party analytics services,
      advertising networks, or data collection platforms by default.
    </p>
    <p class="textiboi">
      If any optional integrations are added in the future, they will be
      explicitly disclosed to users.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">No User Accounts</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      The Focus app does not require or support user accounts, authentication,
      or login systems. You can use the App completely anonymously without
      providing any personal information.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Data Security</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Since all your data is stored locally on your device, the security of
      your data depends on the security measures you have in place on your
      device, including:
    </p>
    <ul class="textiboi">
      <li>Device lock screens and passwords</li>
      <li>Operating system security settings</li>
      <li>Device encryption (if available)</li>
      <li>Physical security of your device</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We recommend ensuring your device has appropriate security measures
      enabled to protect your locally stored data.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Data Backup and Loss</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Because the App stores data locally without cloud backup by default, you
      are responsible for backing up your data. LeonimusT cannot recover lost
      data if:
    </p>
    <ul class="textiboi">
      <li>Your device is lost, stolen, or damaged</li>
      <li>You uninstall the App without backing up your data</li>
      <li>Your device experiences a system failure or data corruption</li>
      <li>You reset or replace your device</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We recommend regularly exporting your focus session data (if the App
      provides this feature) or using your device's built-in backup solutions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 0.9s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      The App does not collect any personal information from anyone, including
      children under 13. Since no data is collected or transmitted by default,
      the App is privacy-friendly for users of all ages.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in
      our practices or for legal, operational, or regulatory reasons. Any
      changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated"
      date.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 1.1s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      Since the Focus app does not collect or store any of your data on our
      servers by default:
    </p>
    <ul class="textiboi">
      <li>You have complete control over your data at all times</li>
      <li>You can delete your data by uninstalling the App</li>
      <li>There is no data to request, export, or delete from our systems</li>
      <li>No consent or permissions are needed beyond what your device
        requires</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Contact Information</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy
      Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:
      <br><br>
      LeonimusT<br>
      <a href="mailto:leo@leonimust.com"
        style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">leo@leonimust.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We will respond to your inquiry as soon as reasonably possible.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 1.3s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Consent</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      By using the Focus app, you acknowledge that you have read and
      understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

